From fb0d35590ff488f4c36a7a8ce4af8fd0caf46d82 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: forgejo-tart-runner <noreply@local>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 03:13:50 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Add tart macOS VM execution backend

Adds a 'tart' label scheme that runs each job inside a disposable Apple
tart macOS VM. Reuses HostEnvironment for file handling (work-root mounted
into the guest and symlinked to an identical path); commands execute via
'tart exec'. VM lifecycle (clone/run/stop/delete) is driven through the
tart CLI, which is installed separately and never bundled.
---
